<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/892121-did-anyone-else-find-the-character-of-neni">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Did anyone else find the character of Neni a bit inconsistent? When Cindy asked Jende to betray Clark, I was surprised by how ready Neni was to support Winston's plan to blackmail Cindy. Up until that point, Neni seemed to have felt nothing but compassion for Cindy's problems and appreciation for her generosity. If that was intended to be a turning point in Neni's relationship with Cindy, it certainly snuck up on me. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
