<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I agree. I read this book for my book group and we all loved it. I find it topical in light of the current situation in our country, especially for th<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I agree. I read this book for my book group and we all loved it. I find it topical in light of the current situation in our country, especially for those who are working toward their "green card" and not only here for asylum. So few of us know the details behind our legal system for all immigrants.<br /><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
