        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1877892158" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2810225433574654766">The immigrant story has been the central theme to quite a lot of contemporary novels these past few years. The release of Imbolo Mbue&apos;s Behold the Dreamers may have first been perceived as another typical immigrant story to join all the others, but actually it&apos;s much more.... For more click the link <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://browngirlreading.com/2017/01/13/behold-the-dreamers/'>https://browngirlreading.com/2017/01/...</a></span>
